   6:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *
   7:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *   This file provides two functions and one global variable to be called from
   8:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *   user application:
   9:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *      - SystemInit(): This function is called at startup just after reset and
  10:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *                      before branch to main program. This call is made inside
  11:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *                      the "startup_stm32g4xx.s" file.
  12:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *
  13:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *      - SystemCoreClock variable: Contains the core clock (HCLK), it can be used
  14:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *                                  by the user application to setup the SysTick
  15:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *                                  timer or configure other parameters.
  16:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *
  17:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *      - SystemCoreClockUpdate(): Updates the variable SystemCoreClock and must
  18:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *                                 be called whenever the core clock is changed
  19:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *                                 during program execution.
  20:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *
  21:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *   After each device reset the HSI (16 MHz) is used as system clock source.
  22:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *   Then SystemInit() function is called, in "startup_stm32g4xx.s" file, to
  23:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *   configure the system clock before to branch to main program.
  24:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *
  25:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *   This file configures the system clock as follows:
  26:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *=============================================================================
  27:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  28:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *        System Clock source                    | HSI
  29:./Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32G4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   *-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
